                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>The pot that Mr. Green gave to me is the same I shewed to Mr. Dodson; it has been in my possession ever since.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17860830-49-person584">
                  JOHN
                   GREEN
               <interp inst="t17860830-49-person584" type="surname" value="GREEN"></interp>
